Paul Sancya Rally in 7th leads to Royals victory 
Kansas City Royals' Eric Hosmer (35) scores on a single by Mike Moustakas during the seventh inning. (AP Photo/Paul Sancya) Posted: Saturday, October 17, 2015 10:49 pm 
KANSAS CITY, Mo. (AP) — The Kansas City Royals kept waiting for Blue Jays ace David Price to give them some hope. 
It turned out to be Toronto’s leaky defense that provided it.     Subscription required
